<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是等待了许久的万圣节！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay8 />今天我到底能收到<delay20 />
多少糖果呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于到来啦！<delay8 />万圣节这一天！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有鼓足气势吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天岛上的大家<delay8 />
都会为了糖果不遗余力哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也做好心理准备来挑战吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能够机敏地行动，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近每天都有<delay8 />
刻苦锻炼腰腿哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会在今天的万圣节展示一下锻炼成果，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就等着看吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">距离万圣节活动开始，<delay20 />
马上就要进入倒计时啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你做好<delay8 />身心准备了吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是<delay8 />要尽全力挑战的哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你别被吓得<delay8 />瘫倒在地啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">万圣节活动终于要开始啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟糕，<delay20 />我激动得颤抖起来了～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />并、<delay8 />并不是因为害怕哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糖果就位，<delay20 />服装就位！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很好！<delay8 />我已经准备万全啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来吧！<delay8 />万圣节！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay20 />我看到外面
稀稀落落地摆着南瓜装饰，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />莫非是为万圣节准备的？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜<delay8 />还挺有分量的，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原先还以为是谁把它当作杠铃来用，<delay20 />
用完就丢在原地了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次我看到<delay8 />南瓜装饰，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都觉得万圣节的脚步更近了些，<delay8 />
让我禁不住心焦啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了能够尽全力将糖果收入囊中，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要在节日当天来临之前，<delay8 />
更加努力地练出轻快的步伐！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="32" />上的装饰多了好多啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />按照这个势头，<delay20 />到了万圣节当天，<delay8 />
我们的<tag a="110" b="32" />就要被南瓜淹没了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到处都是南瓜装饰，<delay8 />都数不清了啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一种万圣节真的就要来了的感觉，<delay20 />
让人好兴奋！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剩下的就是等待节日当天到来！<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除了节日的准备，<delay20 />
你也要做足心理准备哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>